ActIndian Act
SubjectFairford Indian Reserve No. 50, Manitoba ** Grant of Easement **
PrecisOrder (1) consenting to the exercise by MANITOBA of the power to take an interest in lands within FAIRFORD INDIAN RESERVE NO. 50, in Manitoba for flooding protection purposes; and (2) granting to Manitoba the required easement.
